name: Execution Ticket 01
description:
Admits one (1) to the live execution at the SkreedCo Arena on 12-25-21 sponsored by the Artifact Quest Initiative. Holders of this ticket will receive 1/3 camera angles of the execution per ticket held, as well as five (5) nutrition cubes after the corpse has been mechanically separated. Camera angles will have different edition sizes and will be randomly distributed. Holders of all 3 camera angles will receive a 4th angle.

Have fun and enjoy the show!

Created by @alexdelia for Artifact.Quest
2021.
